MCCORMICK PLACE STATION McCormick Place station is a commuter rail station in Chicago underneath McCormick Place , Chicago 's main convention center , that serves the Metra Electric Line north to the Millennium Station and south to University Park , Blue Island , and South Chicago ; and the South Shore Line to Gary and South Bend , Indiana .
The South Shore Line stops here on weekends only .
